overview: A Sci-Fi Action Adventure Comedic Super Hero Episodic  Four teenagers stumble upon an alien spacecraft.  From there skills with computer gaming they are able to steal the craft and wreak havoc around the galaxy. By a slip of the tongue they become known as “The Rabbit Squad”. As they stumble their way, they manage to save the galaxy from impending doom. The galactic order officially proclaims them heroes of the galaxy. Our four heroes make the alien elite do “The Rabbit Dance” to become members of “The Rabbit Squad”.
title: The Rabbit Squad
